examples.en: I think the camera is busted.
He busted his watch when he fell.
They were busted for carrying guns.
She got busted for drug possession.
A bunch of bikers busted up the bar.
Elaine busted up laughing at the sight of him.
examples.ru: При виде его Илейн чуть не лопнула со смеху.

examples.en: Two students got busted by the teacher for smoking in the bathroom.
examples.ru: Учитель застукал двух учеников за курением в туалете.

examples.en: He was busted by U.S. inspectors at the border.
examples.ru: На границе его задержали американские досмотрщики.
